<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Persecution_of_Jews" title="Persecution of Jews">Persecution</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Holocaust" title="The Holocaust">The Holocaust</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_Israel" title="History of Israel">Israel</a></li>
<li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Land_of_Israel" title="Land of Israel">Land of Israel</a></li>
