</tr><tr><th style="padding:0.1em">
<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zionism" title="Zionism">Zionism</a></th></tr><tr><td class="hlist" style="padding:0 0.1em 0.4em">
<ul><li><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Secular_Jewish_music" title="Secular Jewish music">Secular</a></li>
